; Each connector bridges the gap between a boundary wall and a pillar edge,
; turning the pillar pairs into gated archways.
;
; Left gate:  GateL_Top  y=48→255  (above Pillar1)
;             GateL_Bot  y=825→1032 (below Pillar2)
;             Open slot  y=345→735  (390 px — fits player but guards it)
